            <div class="col-3">
                <p>Under Bracken Darrell's 10-year leadership as president and CEO, Logitech has reinvented itself as an award-winning design company, an industry force in pursuit of a sustainable and equitable world and is a leading performer on the Swiss SIX Stock Exchange and several Nasdaq Global Options Markets. During the same period, the company's net sales doubled and profits (net income) more than 13 times.</p>

                <img src="~/Content/img/index/AnyConv.com__user1.png">
                <h3>BRACKEN DARRELL</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3">
                <p>Samantha Harnett As Logitech Global Operations Lead, Prakash Arunkundrum is responsible for all manufacturing, global supply chain, sourcing, and product quality operations. Prakash is also responsible for driving the strategy and execution of Logitech's sustainability initiatives and delivering on Logitech's sustainability commitments in global products and operations.</p>

